        "description": "Experience the excitement of a real Escape Room, right at home. In this challenging and nerve-racking horror two-player edition of the world-famous Escape Room The Game, you work with your teammate to solve puzzles and find hidden clues.<br/><br/>It's a race against time; you only have 60 minutes to escape. In this game you win or lose together. Teamwork is the key to success. If you've never played an Escape Room before, prepare for a completely new experience. Unbelievable how quickly an hour passes in the heat of battle!<br/><br/>Contains 1 introductory adventure (15 minutes tutorial &quot;Bloody Mary&quot;) and 2 complete adventures. To play this game you need a smartphone with the digital Chrono Decoder in the Escape Room The Game app OR the Chrono Decoder from the base game.<br/><br/>House by the Lake<br/>Your car breaks down in the middle of nowhere. Luckily a friendly pump operator offers to fix your car in a day. He even gives you directions to his family&rsquo;s house by the lake where you can spend the night! Unaware of the family&rsquo;s dark secret you set out&hellip;<br/><br/>Little Girl<br/>4 years ago, you&rsquo;ve finally managed to put the Mortician behind bars; a serial killer that killed 9 little girls and left their bodies in horrible poses. Now your niece suddenly disappears. Could this be the work of a copycat? Time to pay the Mortician a visit&hellip;<br/><br/>",
